    "name": "Seeker of the Ruins",
    "steam_appid": 3111070,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111070/extras/06dd6e4cdc904d38b9800a86400bcacf.avif?t=1757521549\" width=650 height=150 /></span><br>在寻找一款独特的解谜探索游戏？你来对地方了。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《遗迹探索者》中踏上史诗之旅，这是一款设定在古代矮人废墟深处的探索冒险游戏。作为一位勇敢的矮人探索者，你的使命是发现失落的宝藏、揭开隐藏的秘密、解决巧妙的谜题，并在危机四伏的古老遗迹中前行。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特色：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111070/extras/6cf885879633836508e6063533d31688.poster.avif?t=1757521549\" width=650 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111070/extras/6cf885879633836508e6063533d31688.webm?t=1757521549\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111070/extras/6cf885879633836508e6063533d31688.mp4?t=1757521549\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>探索</strong>：穿越各种壮丽的古代矮人遗迹。在废墟中前行、收集宝藏并发现隐藏的秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111070/extras/ec3906ab56bd487da7e2ba8e8cc02371.poster.avif?t=1757521549\" width=650 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111070/extras/ec3906ab56bd487da7e2ba8e8cc02371.webm?t=1757521549\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111070/extras/ec3906ab56bd487da7e2ba8e8cc02371.mp4?t=1757521549\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>谜题</strong>：在环境中寻找线索。从解读符文到理解锻造间的布局，逐步开启被遗忘的密室与藏宝点。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111070/extras/064dbdc98d82e85a9d62082d43cdac22.poster.avif?t=1757521549\" width=650 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111070/extras/064dbdc98d82e85a9d62082d43cdac22.webm?t=1757521549\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111070/extras/064dbdc98d82e85a9d62082d43cdac22.mp4?t=1757521549\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>隐藏区域</strong>：发现隐藏在假墙和神秘符号背后的秘密房间与通道。这些区域提供稀有宝藏以及通向更深层秘密的捷径。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111070/extras/6dd8b41d99ffb7e8ffb1f1603d7fc728.poster.avif?t=1757521549\" width=650 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111070/extras/6dd8b41d99ffb7e8ffb1f1603d7fc728.webm?t=1757521549\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111070/extras/6dd8b41d99ffb7e8ffb1f1603d7fc728.mp4?t=1757521549\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>非战斗 &amp; 潜行</strong>：无需武器，仅靠智慧、隐匿与时机躲避危险。躲过古老陷阱、环境威胁和聪明的怪物，在阴影中悄然穿梭，掌握躲避的艺术，保持旅程不被打扰。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111070/extras/10781657a2d5bf32c994fedc13e3a0c1.poster.avif?t=1757521549\" width=650 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111070/extras/10781657a2d5bf32c994fedc13e3a0c1.webm?t=1757521549\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111070/extras/10781657a2d5bf32c994fedc13e3a0c1.mp4?t=1757521549\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>利用道具</strong>：使用各种独特的装置和神秘药剂克服障碍。尝试组合物品来解除陷阱、揭示隐藏铭文或绕过敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你准备好深入废墟，夺回矮人遗失的传承了吗？</p>",
